name: YOLO (TheRealAkatosh)
description:
You only live once so YEET! yourself towards danger cuz why not. Use the bodies of your dead predecessors to solve different puzzles.

Instructions:
Start the game by hitting any key. 
Press A or D key to move left or right.
Space to jump and holding it will make you jump higher.
Press R if your stress and commit sudoku. (Has a 5 second cooldown)
